​  <name>MuseScore</name>
​  <summary>Free music composition and notation software</summary>
​
​  <description>
	<p>
	MuseScore is an open source and free music notation software. For support, contribution, bug reports, visit MuseScore.org.
	</p>
	<p>Features</p>
	<ul>
	<li>WYSIWYG design, notes are entered on a "virtual notepaper"</li>
	<li>TrueType font(s) for printing & display allows for high quality scaling to all sizes</li>
	<li>easy & fast note entry</li>
	<li>many editing functions</li>
	<li>MusicXML import/export</li>
	<li>Midi (SMF) import/export</li>
	<li>MuseData import</li>
	<li>Midi input for note entry</li>
	<li>integrated sequencer and software synthesizer to play the score</li>
	<li>print or create pdf files</li>
	</ul>
​  </description>
